title: GeoRanker

api_list.name: createMonitorLinkedToReport
api_list.description: Creates a monitor linked to a report already created

required_parameters.name: session
required_parameters.description: User session obtained from login method

optional_parameters.name: periodicity
optional_parameters.description: d - Daily, w - Weekly, f - Fortnightly, m - Monthly

optional_parameters.name: isSendEmail
optional_parameters.description: Email alerts on significant changes

api_list.name: createReport
api_list.description: Creates a new report

required_parameters.name: session
required_parameters.description: User session obtained from login method

required_parameters.name: keywords
required_parameters.description: List of keywords. You must specify at least one keyword. The keyword must contain at least 3 characters.

optional_parameters.name: callback
optional_parameters.description: Link to callback

optional_parameters.name: monitorId
optional_parameters.description: Monitor Id

optional_parameters.name: isForMobile
optional_parameters.description: Is this report for mobile platform

optional_parameters.name: isGlobal
optional_parameters.description: True if the report is a country-level report.

optional_parameters.name: isFillCities
optional_parameters.description: If your report has fewer cities than the maxcities, crawler will automatically fill the report cities with the biggest cities from the country.

optional_parameters.name: isUseAlternativeTld
optional_parameters.description: If true, it will always use the TLD.com instead of using the local TLDs for each country.

optional_parameters.name: language
optional_parameters.description: Language

optional_parameters.name: maxCities
optional_parameters.description: Max City count

optional_parameters.name: url
optional_parameters.description: Url. Required with ranktracker type.

optional_parameters.name: totalResults
optional_parameters.description: The maximum amount of results we will crawl. Usually, you want to keep this at 100.

optional_parameters.name: searchEngines
optional_parameters.description: List of Search Engines (google, googlelocal, yahoo, bing, yandex, youtube, naverwebdocs, naverlocal, baidu,googlenews, googleimages). Default: google

optional_parameters.name: countries
optional_parameters.description: List of Country codes

optional_parameters.name: ignoreTypes
optional_parameters.description: This is a list with 2 letter strings that allow you to make crawler completely ignore a search result type. The options are 'OR' (organic), 'GM' (google maps)

optional_parameters.name: regions
optional_parameters.description: List of regions. Example [Asia]
